rows.label: qst701008_msg0001
rows.name:
Everyone! Kaede-chan and I
gathered this. Please take it!

rows.label: qst701008_msg0002
rows.name:
I don't think this is enough
yet... but I wanted to help
in any way I could.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0003
rows.name:
Let's definitely complete the
shelter! I'll do my best too!

rows.label: qst701008_msg0101
rows.name:
For a while, I think I'll stay
in the capital and help my dad.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0102
rows.name:
At a time like this, I feel like
there's something we can do too.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0103
rows.name:
Before, I think I would have just been
scared... but after going to Gula, I
feel like I've changed a little.

rows.label: qst701008_msg0104
rows.name:
Instead of counting the things I
can't do, I learned to find the
things I can do now with Kaede-chan.
